videos.description: Chimezie Metu finds Elijah Stewart on his way to the basket for the big two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: USC's Stewart left open for dunk

videos.description: Jeff Roberson knocks down the 3-pointer to give Vanderbilt their first lead of the game.
videos.headline: Vanderbilt goes up with deep 3-pointer

videos.description: Matthew Fisher-Davis hits the 3-pointer off the long pass from Larry Austin Jr.
videos.headline: Commodores knock down 3-pointer off the break

videos.description: Jonah Matthews hits a 3-pointer in the closing seconds of the first half to finish off a 15-0 Trojans run.
videos.headline: Matthews' 3-pointer caps off USC run to close first half

videos.description: Matthew Fisher-Davis inbounds the ball with less than two seconds on the shot clock and hits the jumper after a pump fake.
videos.headline: Vanderbilt's Fisher-Davis beats shot clock with circus shot

videos.description: Matthew Fisher-Davis makes the 3-pointer off the catch and shoot to extend the Vanderbilt lead.
videos.headline: Fisher-Davis hits another 3-pointer for the Commodores

videos.description: Jordan McLaughlin takes it up the court himself to get the layup and-1.
videos.headline: McLaughlin goes coast-to-coast for USC

videos.description: Riley LaChance makes his way to the basket for the layup and-1.
videos.headline: LaChance drives to the basket to put Vanderbilt back up

videos.description: Jordan McLaughlin crosses over and makes the 3-pointer to tie the game at 80-80.
videos.headline: McLaughlin hits clutch 3-pointer for the Trojans

videos.description: Jordan McLaughlin opens up the scoring in overtime with another 3-pointer.
videos.headline: McLaughlin with another big 3-pointer for USC
